'''AMX'''是美国一家视频切换和控制设备制造商，是[[三星电子|三星电子]]旗下[[哈曼国际工业|哈曼国际工业]]的子公司。

1982年，斯科特·D·米勒（Scott D. Miller）创立了AMX公司。AMX從[[幻燈片投影機|幻灯片投影仪]]遥控器起家<ref>https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=755551&privcapId=25033828</ref>。1988年，AMX发明了世界上第一台用于房间[[自动化技术|自动化]]的触摸屏<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.amx.com/en/news/harman-celebrates-30th-anniversary-of-amx-touch-panels-with-new-streamlined-control-and-room-scheduling-panel-lineup |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-09-10 |archive-date=2019-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724064237/https://www.amx.com/en/news/harman-celebrates-30th-anniversary-of-amx-touch-panels-with-new-streamlined-control-and-room-scheduling-panel-lineup |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年3月21日，[[哈曼国际工业|哈曼国际工业]]以3.65亿美元收购AMX<ref>{{Cite web|title=Baffling 'Batman' Backdoor Busted In Comms Used By Global Governments|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2016/01/21/black-widow-batman-backdoors-amx-harman/#33faa8673d72|accessdate=|author=福布斯|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602222931/http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2016/01/21/black-widow-batman-backdoors-amx-harman/#33faa8673d72|dead-url=no}}</ref>。          

